1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,937
=Episode 19=

3
00:00:19,480 --> 00:00:20,719
Where could it be?

4
00:00:20,719 --> 00:00:21,280
Who's there?

5
00:00:23,120 --> 00:00:23,839
Who are you?

6
00:00:27,679 --> 00:00:28,879
Coroner Xu?

7
00:00:29,280 --> 00:00:29,960
Wushuang?

8
00:00:31,130 --> 00:00:32,079
What are you doing here?

9
00:00:32,159 --> 00:00:32,980
- Are you...
- I...

10
00:00:33,087 --> 00:00:33,840
- I...
- My dear!

11
00:00:34,119 --> 00:00:34,799
My dear!

12
00:00:43,119 --> 00:00:43,759
Wushuang.

13
00:00:44,039 --> 00:00:45,790
You snuck into my room
in the dead of night,

14
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:47,479
struck my acupoints,

15
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:49,439
and started groping me all over!

16
00:00:49,600 --> 00:00:50,159
You...

17
00:00:50,600 --> 00:00:51,520
I never thought...

18
00:00:52,390 --> 00:00:54,240
I never thought
you would have this kind of...

19
00:00:54,880 --> 00:00:56,159
No! I didn't!

20
00:00:59,200 --> 00:00:59,759
I...

21
00:01:00,159 --> 00:01:00,759
Wushuang,

22
00:01:00,759 --> 00:01:02,719
you've really crossed a line this time.

23
00:01:03,037 --> 00:01:03,596
I...

24
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:05,560
Chu Yunchang,

25
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:07,200
why did you swap rooms with Rong?

26
00:01:08,079 --> 00:01:10,359
This room is far too close
to the hot spring.

27
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:12,239
It was so noisy I couldn't sleep.

28
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:14,040
That's why I swapped with Rong.

29
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,000
My dear.

30
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,000
Yes?

31
00:01:16,439 --> 00:01:17,760
I have an idea.

32
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:19,790
Yunchang said Premium Room Six

33
00:01:19,800 --> 00:01:21,560
was too close
to the spring in the backyard.

34
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:23,040
The constant sound of rushing water

35
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:24,400
kept her awake every night.

36
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:26,040
She hasn't been feeling well lately,

37
00:01:26,159 --> 00:01:26,920
and lack of sleep

38
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,400
will only hinder her recovery.

39
00:01:28,519 --> 00:01:30,519
So, she asked to swap rooms with us.

40
00:01:31,159 --> 00:01:32,799
Buyu is in Premium Room Eight.

41
00:01:32,820 --> 00:01:34,000
It's even closer to the water.

42
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:35,480
I can only ask for your help.

43
00:01:35,760 --> 00:01:36,680
That's perfectly fine.

44
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,879
We're happy to trade.

45
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,000
You have my thanks.

46
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:44,680
You did this on purpose.

47
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:45,879
You're up to something!

48
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,480
How are we the ones up to something?

49
00:01:48,239 --> 00:01:50,079
Do you think we're clairvoyant?

50
00:01:50,239 --> 00:01:52,599
Could we have predicted that Deputy Luo

51
00:01:52,719 --> 00:01:55,680
would sneak in
to harass Yunchang tonight?

52
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:56,400
Exactly.

53
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:58,079
I did no such thing!

54
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,200
Wushuang,

55
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:01,200
if Chang hadn't swapped rooms

56
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,439
with my sister and her husband,

57
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,079
what would you have done?

58
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,280
I...

59
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,759
You're a dignified girl.

60
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:11,400
You may look respectable and decent,

61
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:15,039
yet you're harboring ill intentions
toward my sister?

62
00:02:15,479 --> 00:02:17,240
That's quite a refined taste.

63
00:02:18,199 --> 00:02:21,599
I had no idea Deputy Luo
had such peculiar habits.

64
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,360
How progressive.

65
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,639
I do not!

66
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,039
Yu,

67
00:02:33,159 --> 00:02:34,319
I'll tell you the truth.

68
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,039
I only entered that room

69
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,080
to investigate a case.

70
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,520
Weren't you here on vacation?

71
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,960
Of course I'd keep the mission

72
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:42,039
a secret from the Chu family.

73
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:44,039
Then, what exactly are you here for?

74
00:02:47,039 --> 00:02:47,840
To catch her,

75
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,360
the Jade Squirrel!

76
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:02,080
Wow, how terrifying.

77
00:03:03,919 --> 00:03:04,840
No, you...

78
00:03:06,039 --> 00:03:07,400
What's with that reaction?

79
00:03:07,759 --> 00:03:10,800
Wushuang, it's the middle of the night.
We're all exhausted.

80
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:11,879
Stop messing around.

81
00:03:12,199 --> 00:03:13,240
I'm not messing around!

82
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,680
Why does no one believe me?

83
00:03:19,159 --> 00:03:19,960
Deputy Luo,

84
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:22,280
do you have some
personal grievance against me?

85
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,199
We are supposed to be on vacation,

86
00:03:25,199 --> 00:03:26,599
yet you keep coming after me.

87
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:29,960
Chu Yunchang,

88
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,719
don't think your fine acting

89
00:03:34,039 --> 00:03:35,120
can cover your trail.

90
00:03:35,439 --> 00:03:37,039
Then, show us some evidence.

91
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:38,759
The night before last,

92
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:40,840
the Jade Squirrel broke
into the Gate Bureau.

93
00:03:41,039 --> 00:03:41,680
Yu,

94
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,039
you know about this.

95
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:48,240
She entered
my grandfather's room with ill intent

96
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,840
and was wounded by his iron pellets.

97
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:53,199
My grandfather's iron pellets
are legendary in the Martial World.

98
00:03:53,319 --> 00:03:54,800
They target vital points.

99
00:03:55,319 --> 00:03:56,520
Once struck by them,

100
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,960
one would suffer
severe internal and external injuries.

101
00:03:59,319 --> 00:04:01,680
Coincidentally, my guards reported

102
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:04,240
that a middle-aged man

103
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:07,039
purchased a Thousand-year Lingzhi
from Changle Hall

104
00:04:07,439 --> 00:04:08,919
and brought it here to Tangshan.

105
00:04:09,479 --> 00:04:10,800
It was meant to treat her wounds!

106
00:04:15,650 --> 00:04:17,160
There are plenty of  middle-aged men.

107
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,279
What gives you the right
to come after us?

108
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:19,920
Exactly.

109
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,680
Then, how do you explain

110
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:23,300
the scent lingering
in the kitchen's pot?

111
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:25,480
Pseudoginseng and saffron.

112
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,480
That's a treatment
for a very serious injury.

113
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,959
I thought it was something serious.

114
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,120
You must realize

115
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:35,480
that this is a public establishment.

116
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:37,680
If you can come here, anyone can.

117
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,560
Perhaps those were left by someone else.

118
00:04:39,879 --> 00:04:43,120
Are you pinning someone else's leftovers
on us now?

119
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:45,199
Is this how you investigate cases?

120
00:04:46,759 --> 00:04:47,399
Wushuang,

121
00:04:47,959 --> 00:04:49,279
that is a bit of a stretch.

122
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,319
Those are just supporting facts.

123
00:04:52,279 --> 00:04:53,600
The most direct evidence...

124
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,120
is on her body.

125
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:58,500
She must have physical wounds
from my grandfather's strike.

126
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:01,160
So, you snuck

127
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:03,040
into her room tonight to investigate?

128
00:05:03,639 --> 00:05:04,279
Correct.

129
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:06,920
Chu Yunchang,

130
00:05:07,399 --> 00:05:09,040
do you dare to undress

131
00:05:09,319 --> 00:05:10,639
and let us see?

132
00:05:16,639 --> 00:05:18,160
You want me to strip here?

133
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:19,920
Chu Yunchang,

134
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:22,800
don't think you can always
stay one step ahead.

135
00:05:23,759 --> 00:05:25,319
Even if the Thousand-year Lingzhi

136
00:05:25,319 --> 00:05:26,519
healed your internal injuries,

137
00:05:26,879 --> 00:05:28,920
the external marks from the iron pellets

138
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:30,399
won't vanish so quickly.

139
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:31,600
I dare you to

140
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,680
take off your clothes.

141
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:33,800
Do you dare?

142
00:05:34,439 --> 00:05:35,199
Listen, Luo.

143
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:36,680
Don't you go too far.

144
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:39,519
My Yunchang is
a respectable young maiden.

145
00:05:39,700 --> 00:05:41,680
If she is forced to undress
in front of everyone,

146
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:44,560
how will she ever find a husband
after such a disgrace?

147
00:05:44,759 --> 00:05:46,199
Weren't you having an in-law meeting?

148
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:48,240
By that logic,

149
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,560
no one here is a stranger.

150
00:05:50,079 --> 00:05:51,279
What's the big deal

151
00:05:51,279 --> 00:05:52,560
if we take a quick look?

152
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:54,279
Who says we aren't strangers?

153
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:55,600
You are definitely a stranger!

154
00:05:58,199 --> 00:05:58,959
Buyu...

155
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:01,319
Chang,

156
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:02,639
I have an idea.

157
00:06:03,319 --> 00:06:04,680
Go to the inner room

158
00:06:04,959 --> 00:06:06,160
with Wushuang and my sister.

159
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:07,240
It's alright.

160
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:07,959
With Rong there,

161
00:06:07,959 --> 00:06:09,160
you won't be framed.

162
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,639
Besides, doing this

163
00:06:10,959 --> 00:06:12,439
will silence everyone who doubts you

164
00:06:12,439 --> 00:06:13,480
once and for all.

165
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,519
But...

166
00:06:17,519 --> 00:06:18,360
But what?

167
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,360
Stop stalling with these excuses.

168
00:06:21,959 --> 00:06:23,000
Is your conscience clear?

169
00:06:27,199 --> 00:06:27,959
Fine!

170
00:06:28,519 --> 00:06:29,839
Rong, I'm counting on you.

171
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:32,160
Don't worry, I'll be completely fair.

172
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:35,519
Mrs. Mei,

173
00:06:36,690 --> 00:06:38,000
where do you think you're going?

174
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:41,879
I...

175
00:06:43,319 --> 00:06:44,360
I need to find the latrine.

176
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:46,959
Please hold it for a minute.

177
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:51,920
Buyu,

178
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:54,560
please keep the Squire
and Mrs. Mei company,

179
00:06:54,639 --> 00:06:56,839
along with Ms. Zhizhi here.

180
00:06:57,399 --> 00:06:58,439
We'll be right back.

181
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:14,480
Take it off.

182
00:07:16,199 --> 00:07:16,839
You...

183
00:07:17,519 --> 00:07:18,199
Turn around.

184
00:07:18,375 --> 00:07:19,399
We're both women.

185
00:07:19,399 --> 00:07:20,360
What's wrong now?

186
00:07:21,113 --> 00:07:22,512
You groped Rong from head to toe

187
00:07:22,512 --> 00:07:23,512
earlier tonight.

188
00:07:23,759 --> 00:07:25,879
Who knows if you have
some sort of peculiar habit?

189
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,480
I have to look out for myself.

190
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,480
That's enough, Wushuang.

191
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:32,120
Turn around. I will inspect her.

192
00:07:32,319 --> 00:07:33,480
Do you not trust me?

193
00:07:34,639 --> 00:07:35,519
Check closely.

194
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:37,759
Let me help you.

195
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:39,399
No need.

196
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:41,279
I can handle this myself.

197
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,319
Yunchang?

198
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:05,759
Are you all right?

199
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,160
Do you need my help?

200
00:08:11,279 --> 00:08:13,000
Are you stalling?

201
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:16,959
Don't turn around!

202
00:08:21,759 --> 00:08:23,040
I'm warning you, Chu Yunchang.

203
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:24,199
Don't play games with me.

204
00:08:24,199 --> 00:08:25,040
If you keep stalling,

205
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,120
believe me,

206
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:27,600
I'll tear your clothes right off.

207
00:08:27,650 --> 00:08:28,399
You wouldn't dare.

208
00:08:30,319 --> 00:08:31,560
Just you wait and see.

209
00:08:40,150 --> 00:08:41,519
Rong!

210
00:08:43,759 --> 00:08:44,399
Chang!

211
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:45,960
Rong!

212
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,120
Who are you?

213
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:54,080
I'm the Jade Squirrel.

214
00:08:55,399 --> 00:08:57,759
The Squirrel's build
is nothing like yours.

215
00:08:57,759 --> 00:08:59,279
You think we'll just believe

216
00:08:59,279 --> 00:09:00,240
whatever you say?

217
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,399
Who are you, really?

218
00:09:12,559 --> 00:09:13,440
Chu Shan?

219
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,720
Squire Mei, Mrs. Mei,

220
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:17,600
Ms. Yunchang.

221
00:09:18,679 --> 00:09:20,120
I must apologize to you all.

222
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,879
I've been hiding my true identity.

223
00:09:23,279 --> 00:09:23,960
Actually,

224
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:26,559
this distant relative of the Chu family

225
00:09:27,559 --> 00:09:29,799
is the champion of the weak,

226
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:32,320
the personification of justice,

227
00:09:32,559 --> 00:09:35,279
the folks' beacon of hope!

228
00:09:35,559 --> 00:09:37,480
The Jade Squirrel!

229
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:44,919
But since this identity
must stay hidden,

230
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,759
I was worried you wouldn't accept it.

231
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:50,360
Hence, I've kept it a secret to today.

232
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:57,480
I always treated you like a brother.

233
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,320
I can't believe you lied to me.

234
00:09:59,799 --> 00:10:00,720
Exactly!

235
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:02,360
This is outrageous.

236
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:05,200
Yeah! I admired

237
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,240
and trusted you!

238
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,960
How could you lie to me?

239
00:10:08,639 --> 00:10:09,279
Enough!

240
00:10:11,039 --> 00:10:12,200
What a load of nonsense.

241
00:10:14,519 --> 00:10:16,960
Yu, Rong, Coroner Xu,

242
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:18,559
we all know

243
00:10:18,639 --> 00:10:20,639
the Jade Squirrel is clearly a woman.

244
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:23,360
But today, it's suddenly this old man?

245
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:26,279
Your acting is truly pathetic.

246
00:10:28,399 --> 00:10:30,159
Did you really think we'd believe you?

247
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:32,279
Young lady,

248
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:34,200
I won't blame you

249
00:10:34,279 --> 00:10:35,320
for being so ignorant.

250
00:10:35,879 --> 00:10:36,720
You won't believe me?

251
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:37,480
Fine.

252
00:10:37,919 --> 00:10:39,639
Today, I'll let you witness

253
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:42,360
the Sacred Hand Sect's Art of Disguise!

254
00:10:48,279 --> 00:10:48,919
Everyone,

255
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:51,279
we'll cross paths again.

256
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:52,840
Farewell!

257
00:10:58,450 --> 00:10:59,075
(Gentle Breeze of Delight)

258
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:08,879
Moonward Dash!

259
00:11:10,919 --> 00:11:12,399
He really is the Jade Squirrel.

260
00:11:22,025 --> 00:11:23,919
(Ministry of Justice)

261
00:11:23,919 --> 00:11:24,900
The Commissioner declared

262
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:27,240
that Constable Mao Buyu
of the Arrest Corps

263
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:29,720
has solved numerous major cases
with exceptional diligence.

264
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:32,039
His mid-year evaluation
is First Class, Upper Rank.

265
00:11:32,279 --> 00:11:33,080
Starting today,

266
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:34,480
Mao Buyu's promoted to

267
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:37,240
Chief Deputy Constable
of the Gate Bureau.

268
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:38,720
Father,

269
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:39,799
Buyu is now

270
00:11:39,799 --> 00:11:41,960
the primary Deputy Constable
of the Arrest Corps.

271
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:43,399
He is ranked right after Yue Lun.

272
00:11:43,399 --> 00:11:44,720
As long as nothing goes wrong,

273
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:46,480
when Constable Yue
is promoted next year,

274
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:48,720
Buyu will naturally take over
as Chief Constable.

275
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:49,360
That's right.

276
00:11:49,759 --> 00:11:50,919
Despite Buyu's young age,

277
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:53,159
he's already the Seventh Rank officer.

278
00:11:53,399 --> 00:11:55,080
His future is very promising.

279
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:56,759
Father,

280
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:59,039
since Buyu is already
the primary Deputy Constable,

281
00:11:59,039 --> 00:12:01,679
shouldn't we start making
his wedding arrangements?

282
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:05,600
Very well.

283
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:06,919
Buyu,

284
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:09,279
once you've officially
become Chief Constable,

285
00:12:09,519 --> 00:12:11,360
I'll handle the wedding preparations.

286
00:12:14,279 --> 00:12:15,039
Thank you, Father!

287
00:12:16,519 --> 00:12:18,120
Seriously? Are you sure?

288
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,240
Yes!

289
00:12:20,275 --> 00:12:20,759
(Rising Clouds and Dawning Afterglow)

290
00:12:20,759 --> 00:12:21,679
This is great!

291
00:12:25,039 --> 00:12:26,759
Chang, I want to...

292
00:12:28,279 --> 00:12:29,759
What do you want?

293
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,240
I want...

294
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:36,799
I haven't formally
proposed to your family yet.

295
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:37,960
Let's go right now!

296
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:38,480
Come on!

297
00:12:49,919 --> 00:12:50,879
Are you here to propose?

298
00:12:51,879 --> 00:12:52,480
Yes.

299
00:12:59,384 --> 00:13:00,425
It's about time.

300
00:13:00,425 --> 00:13:01,664
What took you so long?

301
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:02,639
Wonderful!

302
00:13:02,639 --> 00:13:04,039
Chang is finally getting married!

303
00:13:04,039 --> 00:13:05,280
Let's get one thing straight.

304
00:13:05,290 --> 00:13:06,440
Since you've proposed today,

305
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:08,200
there's no backing out!

306
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:11,919
Why are you saying that to him?

307
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,500
Do you want me to get married or not?

308
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:14,919
It's nothing.

309
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:18,840
It's a match made in heaven.

310
00:13:19,240 --> 00:13:21,279
Dinner tonight at Bazhen Restaurant
is on me.

311
00:13:21,879 --> 00:13:22,759
Thank you, Mrs. Mei.

312
00:13:24,679 --> 00:13:25,600
Thank you, Auntie.

313
00:13:25,700 --> 00:13:27,101
Don't call me that just yet.

314
00:13:27,175 --> 00:13:28,175
Wait until next year.

315
00:13:28,799 --> 00:13:29,639
After all,

316
00:13:29,639 --> 00:13:31,480
having a Gate Bureau officer
call me "Auntie"

317
00:13:31,480 --> 00:13:32,799
takes some getting used to.

318
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:37,840
Chang, I'm finally going to marry you.

319
00:13:38,519 --> 00:13:39,679
Even if the sky falls,

320
00:13:39,790 --> 00:13:41,000
we're going through with this.

321
00:13:47,620 --> 00:13:49,320
My uncle said
on the 15th of the 9th month,

322
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:50,960
he'd like to invite your father, Rong,

323
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:53,120
and Anran over
to discuss the wedding.

324
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:53,919
Perfect.

325
00:13:54,639 --> 00:13:55,879
I'll tell my father to start

326
00:13:55,879 --> 00:13:57,039
preparing the betrothal gifts.

327
00:13:57,879 --> 00:13:58,720
Later today?

328
00:13:58,720 --> 00:14:00,039
Isn't that a bit early?

329
00:14:00,039 --> 00:14:01,320
Anran mentioned

330
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:03,600
that weddings involve
a lot of tedious details.

331
00:14:03,740 --> 00:14:05,080
It's better to be early than late.

332
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:07,600
Whatever you say.

333
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:12,159
Have a bite.

334
00:14:12,799 --> 00:14:14,279
You have some.

335
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:16,679
Are you two glued at the hip?

336
00:14:17,700 --> 00:14:18,639
Mind your own business.

337
00:14:18,759 --> 00:14:19,639
We're talking.

338
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:22,799
You're just rubbing it in
because I'm single, aren't you?

339
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:28,720
Who's that?

340
00:14:29,519 --> 00:14:30,279
Tastes good, right?

341
00:14:39,919 --> 00:14:41,440
Excuse me, is this...

342
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:42,840
Yes, yes, it is.

343
00:14:43,159 --> 00:14:44,360
I haven't even asked yet.

344
00:14:44,690 --> 00:14:46,039
Whatever it is, the answer is yes.

345
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:47,320
Gentleman,

346
00:14:47,919 --> 00:14:50,159
are you aware that you're handsome?

347
00:14:50,679 --> 00:14:51,360
Thank you.

348
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:53,720
Excuse me, is Ms. Chu Yunchang in?

349
00:14:55,159 --> 00:14:56,600
What business do you have with her?

350
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:59,080
(Shen Liefeng, Xichuan Bandit Prince)
I am Shen Liefeng.

351
00:14:59,399 --> 00:15:00,960
I am Ms. Chu Yunchang's

352
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:02,679
betrothed husband.

353
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:09,080
Madam! Madam!

354
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:11,799
Madam!

355
00:15:11,799 --> 00:15:12,639
Bad news!

356
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:14,399
What's all the panic about?

357
00:15:14,519 --> 00:15:15,799
Someone's sent a formal petition!

358
00:15:16,120 --> 00:15:16,919
A petition?

359
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:18,159
Let me see that.

360
00:15:20,720 --> 00:15:21,279
Dismissed.

361
00:15:22,625 --> 00:15:24,800
(Shen Liefeng follows his father's order
to propose to the Sacred Hand Sect.)

362
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:25,960
The Xichuan Bandit Prince?

363
00:15:28,039 --> 00:15:28,600
Here.

364
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:35,200
Who is this lunatic?

365
00:15:35,200 --> 00:15:36,759
Trying to take advantage of us?

366
00:15:37,159 --> 00:15:38,200
Let's just talk.

367
00:15:38,519 --> 00:15:39,720
Don't start getting physical.

368
00:15:39,720 --> 00:15:41,159
You're harassing a respectable woman.

369
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:42,399
I'm arresting you right now!

370
00:15:43,039 --> 00:15:44,759
I'm not joking.

371
00:15:47,639 --> 00:15:49,519
(Marriage Contract)
I have the marriage contract.

372
00:15:50,759 --> 00:15:51,679
A marriage contract?

373
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:58,759
The elder Master Chu wrote this

374
00:15:58,759 --> 00:16:00,399
after he lost a bet to my father.

375
00:16:00,759 --> 00:16:03,039
(Marriage Contract: I, Chu Zhongtian,)
It's a contract he signed and sealed.

376
00:16:03,799 --> 00:16:06,399
(agree to the marriage of our families.)
It's all written in black and white.

377
00:16:07,500 --> 00:16:09,575
(With no regrets. Signed, Chu Zhongtian)

378
00:16:28,112 --> 00:16:31,387
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

379
00:16:31,425 --> 00:16:34,300
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

380
00:16:34,800 --> 00:16:40,518
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

381
00:16:41,700 --> 00:16:45,020
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

382
00:16:45,150 --> 00:16:48,070
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

383
00:16:49,238 --> 00:16:54,478
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

384
00:16:55,700 --> 00:16:58,093
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

385
00:16:58,093 --> 00:17:01,743
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

386
00:17:01,812 --> 00:17:05,302
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

387
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:08,375
♪To the ends of time♪

388
00:17:08,375 --> 00:17:11,750
♪The moon traces your face♪

389
00:17:11,937 --> 00:17:15,525
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

390
00:17:15,525 --> 00:17:21,765
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

391
00:17:22,100 --> 00:17:25,315
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

392
00:17:25,600 --> 00:17:29,138
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

393
00:17:29,425 --> 00:17:32,450
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

394
00:17:32,450 --> 00:17:35,550
♪On our way to forever♪

395
00:17:35,550 --> 00:17:39,400
♪The moon traces your face♪

396
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:42,760
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

397
00:17:42,950 --> 00:17:48,910
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

398
00:17:49,987 --> 00:17:59,627
♪Just to be with you♪
